title: Ep. 1102 - Daya Talks To Ajay - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha accuses Daya of being manipulative and calls her cunning. Hurt, she tells him that she will call her brother away from home - Ajay Devgn.

title: Ep. 1103 - Himmatwala - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: When Daya calls up Ajay to tell him about Jetha hurting her, he comes to the society to see what is going on and Jetha apologizes.

title: Ep. 1104 - Jetha's Prank - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha sticks a thepla on Iyer's back and sees the fun as Iyer is chased around by Sheru. Iyer is scared for his life and starts running.

title: Ep. 1105 - Popatlal's Dreams Of Marriage - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Yesterday’s walk in the park was very exciting, for Sheru and everyone met Pari. Popatlal is expecting Pari’s parents to come for him with a marriage proposal. Is finally Popatlal going to be happily married?

title: Ep. 1106 - A Dog House - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide gets romantic with Madhvi - Female members of Gokuldham society decide to build a Dog House for Sheru but Bhide has an option. Chameli Bhai gets introduced to Gokuldham members in regards to building a Dog House for Sheru.

title: Ep. 1107 - Sheru Goes Missing - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sheru goes missing - All the members of Gokuldham society are searching Sheru in the colony. Jethalal, Taarak, Popatlal, Bhide and Mr. Iyer file a missing complaint of Sheru in the police station and also request Chalu Pandey to search Sheru.

title: Ep. 1108 - Popatlal Is Rude To Chalu Pandey - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak's master plan to find Sheru - Popatlal, Bhide and Jethalal give more information about Sheru to Inspector Chalu Pandey. Popatlal talks rudely with Chalu Pandey. All the Female members of Gokuldham society are eagerly waiting for Sheru.

title: Ep. 1109 - The Advertisement - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal is searching for Sheru far and wide. Jetha decides to give a prize of 5 Lakh rupees to anyone who finds Sheru and brings him back home safely.

title: Ep. 1110 - The Kidnappers - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Changu and Mangu get special treatment - Jethalal is immensely missing Sheru. All the members of Gokuldham society are extremely happy and excited as Shery returns to Gokuldham society. Kidnappers have entered in Gokuldham society.

title: Ep. 1111 - The Confession - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Changu and Mangu apologize to Jethalal and also reveals a shocking truth to all the members of Gokuldham society. Inspector Chalu Pandey gets angry with Jethalal.

title: Ep. 1112 - The Decision - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya immensely misses Sheru - Sheru reveals his final decision. Sheru's owner Robert assures Jethalal and other Gokuldham members that they can come to meet Sheru whenever they want.

title: Ep. 1113 - Emergency At Roshan's Place - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Emergency in Roshan's house - Jethalal feels prou that he caught the bag with one hand. All the members of Gokuldham society are trying to catch Googl who is strictly disagreeing to go to School until and unless Sodhi does not wish him all the best.

title: Ep. 1114 - The Trip To Amritsar - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak tries to solve Roshan's problem - Daya, Roshan and Bhide rush to Taarak Mehta's house as Roshan urgently wants to leave for Amritsar. Taarak tries to solve Roshan's problem. Jethalal, Baagha and Natu Kaka end up in comical argument.

title: Ep. 1115 - A Task For Bagha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal gives a unique task to Baagha - All the members of Gokuldham society are taking extra care of Googi as Roshan and Sodhi are in Amritsar. Baagha assures Jethalal that he will complete his task. Bapuji gets scared of Googi.

title: Ep. 1116 - Jetha Shares The Secret - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha gets a gift for Gogi because Roshani is not here. It was Daya's idea to get the gift. Babita and Iyer didn't know anout this so Jetha tells them everything.
